      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARD LEAF (4) ran below expectations last time at Naracoorte, finishing sixth after jumping inside $4. Best figures measure up nicely, so can quickly forgive. STAR CASINO (2) returned to winning ways last time out, running away with an impressive 3.5 lengths win over this track and trip. Isaac Sit in the saddle again and despite getting up in the weights he should go very well. THE LAST DANCE (1) got too far back here last time and never came on but was a determined winner two back at Port Lincoln. Will go very close if he can replicate his turf form on the dirt. FOX DUNNETT (8) scored two runs back then was well in commission last time but could only manage to finish fifth here. Finds a nice race and can bounce back.",
